node.text: The highly-anticipated album is now set to release on August 15. The date was confirmed by an iTunes album preview page. The album was predicted to release following the end of ’Ye’s second listening event but to no surprise no album was released. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to get the “whoopity-scoop.”

node.text:
@hypebeastcarclub: @porsche has revealed more details on its upcoming All-Electric Mission R Concept study. Similar in size to the Porsche 718 Cayman, the Mission R is able to put out 671 horsepower when in race mode. The motor runs on an 80 kWh battery capacity and is able to supply up to 45 minutes of on-track action. Other details include a bodymade of natural-fiber-reinforced plastic, a large rear spoiler, aggressive concave wheels, and more.⁠⁠
Photo: Porsche

node.text:
@hypebeaststyle: For Prototype Research_Series 05, @stoneisland_official has created a trench coat using its classic Raso cotton. This material has then been bonded to non-woven fabric with a nanometric copper layer. Thanks to the copper’s natural oxidation characteristics, each jacket will change its look depending on the conditions it is exposed to. The collection is currently on show at an installation at Milan Design Week and will run until September 10.⁠⁠
Photo: Stone Island

@hypebeastcarclub: @supremenewyork is geared to release one of its wildest collaborative accessories to date – a set of box logo-branded spinner rims.⁠⁠ In collaboration with @dubwheels, the 24" x 9" Dub spinners are constructed of forged 6061 aluminum alloy and feature a vivid red/white custom exterior fascia, along with a polished rim lip in an overall convex design. ⁠⁠
Video: Supreme ⁠

node.text:
@hypebeastcarclub: For our latest installment of 'DRIVERS,' we spoke with the founder of @illest @mrk.rcnl about his pristine 1997 Porsche Carrera 4S  993, his appreciation of cars being adopted by streetwear, where the culture’s going, and more. Hit the link in bio for the full feature.⁠⁠
Photo: Brooklyn Arcenal⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by HYPEBEAST on September 08, 2021 tagging @mrk.rcnl, @illest, and @hypebeastcarclub. May be an image of 1 person, standing, car, outdoors and text that says 'HYPEBEAST DRIVERS MARK ARCENAL A'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 08, 2021. May be an image of car and text that says '" The Carrera 4S 993 was one of the first diecast models I owned and modified. I've always wanted to own C4S because of its wide body non-turbo shape. It looked and drove so well when my friend let me take it for spin a few years ago. In the years since started inquiring he's only added 3k miles to it. now has 44k miles.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 08, 2021. May be an image of car and text that says 'CallediEverything " acquired it in 2021 but have been trying to buy it for almost three years from a friend. Every year I'd ask him to sell to me and offered to him more than few times. He'd always say 'no' but recently he said, to my surprise, 'make better offer' and so did. He picked it up from his barn full of cars in Lodi, CA and tossed me the keys.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 08, 2021. May be an image of car and text that says 'f 1 " When started ILLEST, would always use my cars in photoshoots even they were in build mode. Cars became a part of our brand unintentionally. These days, cars are used in every brand's lookbook which is nice to see.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 08, 2021. May be an image of car and text that says 'Carrera CollectEverything ything " What's great about this car is that it's lived within a 10-mile radius its entire life. I'm the second owner.'.

Photo by HYPEBEAST on September 08, 2021. May be an image of car and text that says '" There will always be the culture surrounding the automotive world as long as the manufacturers keep making well thought-out cars. think electric cars are great but need to be designed well in order to keep that culture alive.'.

node.text:
@hypebeastkicks: A trio of @adidas YEEZY 500s are slated to drop in the coming months. Fans can expect two new colorways to be added to the ever-growing 500 family — titled “Clay Brown” and "Ash Grey” — while those that missed out on the "Utility Black" iteration previously will get another chance. Each pair will retail for $200 USD. ⁠
Photo: @yeezymafia

node.text:
@hypebeastcarclub: @mercedesbenz has revealed the VISION AVTR with brain-computer interfaces (BCI), meaning the car can be controlled by the power of thought. A BCI device is attached to the user’s head which subsequently measures brain waves that send information to the car, in turn telling it what to do. Learn more about the technology via the link in bio.⁠⁠
Photo: Mercedes-Benz

@hypebeastkicks: @vetements_official has dropped two pairs of teddy bear-inspired slippers for the cold season ahead. Both slippers are made from fleece, one features a panda bear design while the other features a wild cat design spotted in brown and black. Details include side velcro fastenings and black rubber outsoles. Pick up a pair now via the brand’s website for approximately $1,884 USD. ⁠⁠
Photo: VETEMENTS

@hypebeastmusic: Challenge accepted. @champagnepapi was inspired to drop a bar about @giannis_an34 on ‘CLB’ after a fan Tweet. “Drake working Antetokounmpo into a line is gonna be tricky but he’ll figure out something,” a fan named Graydon Gordian tweeted out on July 20. The rapper rose to the challenge with a reference on “7am On Bridle Path: ” “Don’t move like a puto / Could at least keep it a buck like Antetokounmpo.”⁠
